    <data key="d0">CloudHealth by VMware: Secure State. Manages Over 50M Assets from Billions of Events on AWS</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6EUknQqaV1w</data>
    <data key="d2">Handles billions of events daily to secure 50M+ cloud assets. Uses Amazon Neptune for graph-based resource modeling, supplemented by Elasticsearch and DynamoDB. Employs a custom Sharder service to dynamically load balance write streams based on real-time CloudWatch metrics.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
